ivered to Client. Once the Album has been delivered, Photographer shall have no further obligation to preserve the images of the Event, regardless of the form of media in which they are stored.</p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; white-space: pre-wrap; cursor: text; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; white-space: pre-wrap; cursor: text; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">20. Promotion. </span>I/we hereby give permission for Photographer to use my/our name/s and photographic likeness in all forms and media for advertising, trade, promotional and any other lawful purposes such as promotion and marketing.</p>
